graph TB
    subgraph "TrustyAI Service Operator"
        Operator[TrustyAI Service Operator<br/>Go Controller]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]
        Operator -->|health checks| WebhookServer
    end

    subgraph "TrustyAI Service Deployment"
        TrustyAIService[TrustyAI Service<br/>Quarkus App<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
        TrustyAIService -.->|sidecar| OAuthProxy
    end

    subgraph "LMEval Job Resources"
        LMEvalJob[LMEval Job Pod<br/>Batch]
        LMEvalDriver[LMEval Driver<br/>Init Container]
        LMEvalDriver -->|manages| LMEvalJob
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        TrustyAIServiceCR[TrustyAIService CR<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
        LMEvalJobCR[LMEvalJob CR<br/>trustyai.opendatahub.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Monitoring & Mesh"
        ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitor<br/>Prometheus]
        VirtualService[VirtualService<br/>Istio]
        DestinationRule[DestinationRule<br/>Istio]
    end

    User[User/Administrator] -->|creates| TrustyAIServiceCR
    User -->|creates| LMEvalJobCR

    TrustyAIServiceCR -->|watched by| Operator
    LMEvalJobCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates/manages| TrustyAIService
    Operator -->|creates| OAuthProxy
    Operator -->|creates| LMEvalJob
    Operator -->|creates| ServiceMonitor
    Operator -->|creates| VirtualService
    Operator -->|creates| DestinationRule

    TrustyAIService -->|stores data| Storage[PVC or Database<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL]

    Operator -->|patches| KServeInferenceService[KServe InferenceService]
    Operator -->|patches| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Deployment]

    ModelMesh -->|sends inference data| TrustyAIService
    KServeInferenceService -->|monitored by| TrustyAIService

    Prometheus[Prometheus] -->|scrapes via| ServiceMonitor
    ServiceMonitor -->|targets| TrustyAIService

    ExternalClient[External Client] -->|HTTPS/443| OpenShiftRoute[OpenShift Route]
    OpenShiftRoute -->|HTTPS| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|HTTP| TrustyAIService

    LMEvalJob -->|downloads models| HuggingFace[Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    LMEvalJob -->|stores results| PVC[PVC Storage]

    Operator -->|integrates with| Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queue]
    Kueue -.->|manages| LMEvalJob

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2
    style TrustyAIService fill:#4a90e2
    style OAuthProxy fill:#f5a623
    style TrustyAIServiceCR fill:#7ed321
    style LMEvalJobCR fill:#7ed321
    style KServeInferenceService fill:#e8e8e8
    style ModelMesh fill:#e8e8e8
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8
    style HuggingFace fill:#e8e8e8
    style Kueue fill:#e8e8e8
    style Storage fill:#f5a623
